::Astroblast/Switchblade::

Immediatly after Megatron's blast, Astroblast turns around, heading 
back towards the Wild C.A.T.S. Suttle. He fires twice at each as 
he passes them over head, "Heading back Megatron, I am 
weakened from the plasma surge."

Switchblade perks up as he hears Astroblast say that they are 
coming back. He thinks to himself, <Soon I will be able to work on 
my future creation at the lab...> and then to all, "How long till we 
get there?"

"Shut upm, Switchblade," an annoyed Astroblast says over the 
speakers, "Sit down, and shut up." 

"Blah blah blah," replies Switchblade, as he procedes to sit down 
in the command chair, stretch his legs out on the console. "I still 
say these are nice chairs,"

"GET OUT OF THE CHAIR." says Astroblast forecefully, "I'm sure 
Motormaster, or Megatron would be more than happy just toss out 
some dead weight, namely you. Wouldn't you, Motormaster?" His 
voice ends smugly.

Switchblade ignores Astroblast and closes his eyes. "Hehe."

"Motormaster, toss him out." says Astroblast coldly, "Enough 
said."
